@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zjugaz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.73) - v1))
    v2 = ((v0 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.55)) * tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(v1))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
